title: Just Looking For JTT with Franz Szony
description:
Photographer Franz Szony joins Trixie and Katya to delve into his surrealist portraits that mix glamor with dreamlike visuals. 
Franz explains the creative process behind his unique style that includes everything from eye-popping colors to crowns of penises. 
Also, Katya wants Franz to photograph her wake.

To follow Franz Szony: @FranzSzony
To follow Trixie: @TrixieMattel
To follow Katya: @Katya_Zamo
To listen to our podcast on YouTube: http://bit.ly/TBATBYT
